This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on planning the motion trajectory of robots in manufacturing tasks. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a possible sub-category as it may involve image processing for the fabrication process. Control Systems (cs.SY) is another possible sub-category as it deals with optimizing the motion of the robotic system. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible sub-categories as they may involve using optimization algorithms to plan the trajectory.
